name: Time - Prelude 1
description:
Time. 
I've always been fascinated how time is woven into the fabric of the universe & how time affects the material world around us. Time will be my main theme as I delve into to the creative possibilities of #NFTs in 2022. 

This photo of the inner workings of an old, timeworn watch is the 1st prelude to my explorations.  (Resolution: 8629x5691px)
